The evidence with the title 'Most heroin in U.S. now comes across Mexican border, Rob ... ' says Mar 14, 2016  ... So when Portman said that most of the heroin in America comes from Mexico 's border , we were skeptical. Portman, it turns out, has done his homework. The Drug Enforcement Administration 's National Drug Threat Assessment Of 2015 says that Mexico is the primary supplier of heroin to the United States . 
